## Create an account

Create a sub account under the master account

> Definition

```shell
POST https://api.zoom.us/v2/accounts
```

> Example Request

```shell
$ curl https://api.zoom.us/v2/accounts \
   -d '{
    "email": "string",
    "first_name": "string",
    "last_name": "string",
    "password": "string",
    "options": {
        "share_rc": "boolean",
        "room_connectors": "string",
        "share_mc": "boolean",
        "meeting_conntectors": "string",
        "pay_mode": "string"
    }
}'
```

> Example Response

```text
201 Created
```

Body Arguments | &nbsp;
--- | ---
email **required** | User's email address.
first_name **required** | User's first name.
last_name **required** | User's last name.
password **required** | User's password.
options.share_rc | Enable Share Virtual Room Connector.
options.room_connectors | Virtual Room Connector, multiple value separated by comma.
options.share_mc | Enable Share Meeting Connector.
options.meeting_conntectors | Meeting Connector, multiple value separated by comma.
options.pay_mode | User's password.<div class="enum">`master` Master Account holder pays<br/>`sub` Sub Account holders pays<br/></div>

